본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap (modality-policy). hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 orphan drug policy 라는 정책-경제 framework 에 어떻게 (한정) fit 하는지 cross-axis mapping + supplementary in-silico evidence + 정책 instrument candidate inventory.

(Distinct from 모든 disease entries — orphan drug policy = 희귀질환 약물 개발 인센티브 framework + 임상 + 규제 + 가격 정책 + market exclusivity. 1983 Orphan Drug Act US + 2000 EU regulation + 1972 JP + 2016 PMDA Sakigake + 2020 FDA Rare Pediatric Disease + 한국 2003 희귀질환관리법. 양자-VQE 의 직접 fit 한정 — modality 가 정책-경제. cross-axis mapping = disease_*  희귀 질환 enabler framework.)

scope:
- 희귀질환 정의 (US <200,000 + EU <5/10,000 + 한국 <2만)
- Orphan Drug Designation (ODD)
- 7-year market exclusivity (US Orphan)
- tax credit + grant + waived FDA fee
- accelerated approval pathway
- breakthrough therapy designation
- regenerative medicine advanced therapy (RMAT)
- priority review voucher (Tropical + Pediatric Rare + Material Threat)
- adaptive trial design (small N)
- N-of-1 IND framework (cross-n_of_1)
- patient registry + natural history study
- real-world evidence (RWE)
